1.title: 1° live show spring 2013
1.plot: Opening day at the `Sage Outdoor Adventure ranch in Vail Colorado finds Cole and Sara returning from a romantic trip to New Zealand on opening day. Sold out tours and a new crew struggle to get over thirty new snowmobiles tuned up and the trails groomed. ~The day starts in a frantic and goes downhill as a tourist has a bad wreck into a barb wire fence and then proceeds to get lost near darkness.
